text: The Midsund Bridge () is a reinforced concrete arch bridge that crosses the Midsundet strait between the islands of Otrøya and Midøya in Molde Municipality, Møre og Romsdal county, Norway. The bridge runs between the village of Midsund on Otrøya island to Leirvika on Midøya island.
